  "detailed_description": "<h1>More My Games...</h1><p><br><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Story</u></h2></strong><br><br>Once upon a time, there was an unlucky girl named Cinderella. She's beautiful and kind. <br>However, her stepmother didn't like her one little bit and treated her as a slave.<br><br>One day a letter of invitation was arrived.<br>Telling that a ball was to be held at the palace and the Prince would choose a girl to become his wife.<br><br>She made every effort to get rid of all troubles to go to the ball.<br>Unfortunately, it happened that she saw the King was murdered by the Prince.<br>The Prince claimed that Cinderella killed the King and try to framed her up.<br>Finally, Cinderella was arrested and locked in the dungeon...<br><br>Can she escape from the dungeon? Cinderella need your help!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>GamePlay</u></h2></strong><br>Cinderella Escape! is a 3D Action Puzzle Game.<br>Use the 3 actions to solve the Puzzle and reach the exit.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/408000/extras/742bbf44c638621fc357869d7ff533fd.avif?t=1697814610\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>Keyboard + Mouse layout<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/408000/extras/ebcf982c666a3de6640f739641907dcb.avif?t=1697814610\" width=620 height=348 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Story</u></h2></strong><br><br>Once upon a time, there was an unlucky girl named Cinderella. She's beautiful and kind. <br>However, her stepmother didn't like her one little bit and treated her as a slave.<br><br>One day a letter of invitation was arrived.<br>Telling that a ball was to be held at the palace and the Prince would choose a girl to become his wife.<br><br>She made every effort to get rid of all troubles to go to the ball.<br>Unfortunately, it happened that she saw the King was murdered by the Prince.<br>The Prince claimed that Cinderella killed the King and try to framed her up.<br>Finally, Cinderella was arrested and locked in the dungeon...<br><br>Can she escape from the dungeon? Cinderella need your help!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>GamePlay</u></h2></strong><br>Cinderella Escape! is a 3D Action Puzzle Game.<br>Use the 3 actions to solve the Puzzle and reach the exit.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/408000/extras/742bbf44c638621fc357869d7ff533fd.avif?t=1697814610\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>Keyboard + Mouse layout<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/408000/extras/ebcf982c666a3de6640f739641907dcb.avif?t=1697814610\" width=620 height=348 /></span>",
